Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谷山麻衣 高中一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.37,0:00:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在做着狩灵师的兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然查清楚了吵闹鬼的原因是人偶美美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但从那时起 美美的复仇也开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们调查了森下家宅邸的历任所有者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然发现8岁左右的孩子曾经一个个地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋认为是孩子们的灵魂变成地缚灵附在美美身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫来了约翰和真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试净灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚开始净灵后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.50,0:00:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个黑影是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:00:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.97,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,档案 2     {\r}{\u1}{\fs40}玩偶之家{\r}  {\fs35}#3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后 和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明摄像头里照到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别罗嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚你才是 快走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对阻挠者决不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房子是填了井以后盖的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好老的井啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿有女人的灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:03:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜伏在其中深处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装作母亲的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召唤着孩子们的灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们虽然想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是迷路了 走不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 美美也在这儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美 立花雪子虽然是孩子们的头目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实很痛苦悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说不想再做这样的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来 这井像一直延伸到地底一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在深邃的地下 孩子们的灵困在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人在寻找自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此才召集了这么多孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么后面拜托我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我行我素的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋回来之前除灵看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这次就轮到你们两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来挑战一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先告诉你们 那可是很强的灵噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚和约翰守着礼美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此地暂为祭场 清洗污垢 祓除不祥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭建神篱 诚心祷告...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫子这家伙 竟然说她害怕硬拉我来陪她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也叫灵能力者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:05:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然变冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是从哪儿...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在治理八大洲之国的现世之神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}【此两句出自《祝词中臣寿词】
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大倭根子天皇陛下的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫子 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫子？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人碰了我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 你是巫女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻 麻衣...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚 我的脚...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣...！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是礼美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿的孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 那个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就是不能跟那个人走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子的母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在林就下去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我掉到井里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？被人拐走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子大概被那个男人拐走就没再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她的妈妈就投井了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是灵能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的梦哪有什么意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好被你说中也不一定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还无法判断真假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 总觉得这个梦有什么特殊含义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是跟平常一样的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能救礼美她们么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们可要努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 重放之前的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 你回来了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才站在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是正体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么会在这儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不守着礼美不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋说没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上就能了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原小姐 那帮家伙们动静如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在起居室里 还没到宾馆去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松崎小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你做防止灵进入的符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起在屋里贴满符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宅子里设立结界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把富子找回来给那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 富子已经...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 把富子本人带回来已经不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只要不把富子带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人就不会甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 你打算把礼美...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键问题在于那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把她引出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣还被她拉到井里去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不是应该考虑一下自身安全问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就不管礼美了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却这副狼狈相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是这种水平的灵能者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄自行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我们都会被地缚灵掠走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信不信是你们的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣也是 想回去的话就随便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够为难的啊 你们的社长大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然小恋那样说 就证明他已胸有成竹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为 为什么真砂子这么肯定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然真砂子都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就相信小恋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比什么都不做好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都倒下时 我好歹留下来给你们收尸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 我们按照小恋所说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在房间里贴满了符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 贴符咒有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让大家无法从这房子里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把鬼门打开 把灵放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事都无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他干吗老一副自以为是的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是小恋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 鬼门是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼门是屋子的东北方向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是恶灵容易进来的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚和松崎小姐去鬼门守着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让出来的灵分散开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时减少灵的数量 把那女人拉出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰你去起居室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那边的灵分散开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那最重要的除灵工作谁来做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以天父之名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许我以你之名祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净灵是要跟灵对话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断绝他们对尘世的执念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这工作只有灵媒师能做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋不是灵媒师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却打算净灵的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除灵和净灵有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说服灵 让他们悔改的叫做净灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分青红皂白杀掉灵的叫做除灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望他们除灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不要在我的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对真砂子来说 灵和人类看起来都是一样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在拉我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初 有了语言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,语言与神同在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原小姐 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵们在四处逃窜 数量减少了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边哭泣着 边向着起居室逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不能把小孩子们的灵进行净灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那女人在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出 出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有富子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些孩子不是富子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放他们自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家想回到真正的母亲身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的孩子在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你召集来的孩子们都带走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温柔的光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了 她们升天了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 事情解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也说要尽早赶回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 撤退完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 那木板是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人形？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒的稻草人的原型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把做成人的形状的桐木
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作要诅咒的人本身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那不是诅咒人的方法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓咒术 一定是有黑白两种的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白咒术救人 黑咒术害人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往往同一咒法兼有黑白两面性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密教的“怨敌退散”也可以有正邪两种使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人形就是装有灵魂的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如用人形来代表麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人形受伤的话 麻衣自己也会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人形和本体的关系就是这么密切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表富子的人形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那女人才以为找回了富子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现了愿望而升天了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你居然真会做人形啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去就是为了做这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做人形需要知道富子的生卒年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人名叫大岛广
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子是她的独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子某天失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年后 她的尸体在池子里浮上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 大岛广的家被拆毁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来建起来的 就是这幢房子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富子是被拐走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以女人才跳井自杀的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 这屋子里已经没有灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道从一开始就打算净灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到小恋是个阴阳师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴阳师？就是那个安倍什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然想出做富子的人形来净灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么高明的办法 只有阴阳师可以做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害啊 阴阳师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得他有点帅了哦
